osis, and Travel Psychosis. This classification underscores the clinical relevance of these disorders and provides a standardized approach to diagnosis and treatment. The inclusion of these entities in CCMD-3 highlights their importance in mental health practice and the need for awareness and understanding among healthcare providers. [Data: Relationships (1414, 1412, 1413)]"], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-v3"}}}